data.description: This is where you find the perfect blend of comfort and convenience in this 4-bedroom, 3-bathroom home nestled in the rapidly growing area of Estero but within the gates of the Westbrook community. With just under 2,000 sqft of living space and offering a spacious retreat. It's sought after location off Three Oaks Parkway provides easy access to I-75 and just a short distance from FGCU, RSW International Airport, Miromar Outlets, Hertz Arena home of the Everblades Hockey team and an array of dining and shopping options. The home itself boasts tall doors, a spacious kitchen with granite counters and espresso cabinetry, and plank tile throughout the main living areas. Enjoy the elegance of large tray ceilings in the living room and unwind in the expansive screened back lanai with extended pavers. The owner's suite features a generous walk-in shower and closet, while the split floor plan ensures privacy with guest bedrooms upfront, one being an ensuite. Don't miss the opportunity to call this Westbrook gem your home. You can relax pool side or around the fire pit at the amenity center or get a great sweat in at the state of the art gym!
